
  <div class="border-top-0">
    <p>
      Obtain CLO wallet address at <a href="https://ethereumproject.github.io/etherwallet/" target="_blank">https://ethereumproject.github.io/etherwallet/</a>
    </p>
    <p>Download <a href="https://github.com/ethereum-mining/ethminer/releases" target="blank">ethminer</a>
      for
      you operation system</p>
    <h4><img src="/img/windows.svg" height="20"> Windows</h4>
    <p> Create <code>miner.bat</code> file with following content and run it.</p>
    <pre><code>
setx GPU_FORCE_64BIT_PTR 0
setx GPU_MAX_HEAP_SIZE 100
setx GPU_USE_SYNC_OBJECTS 1
setx GPU_MAX_ALLOC_PERCENT 100
setx GPU_SINGLE_ALLOC_PERCENT 100
<kbd>&lt;path to miner&gt;</kbd>/ethminer.exe -F http://sg.clo.epool.network:8888/<kbd>&lt;wallet&gt;</kbd>/<kbd>&lt;worker&gt;</kbd> -G --farm-recheck 200
          </code></pre>
    <p>
      <code>&lt;wallet&gt;</code> is your CLO wallet address, example:
      <code>0x81029273484ed1167910dd38f7b73000d342f3cf</code>.
      <br>
      <code>&lt;worker&gt;</code> is custom name for worker, example : <code>rig01</code>,
      <code>rig02</code>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="border-top-0">
    <h4><img src="/img/linux.svg" height="20"> Linux</h4>
    <p>
      Create <code>miner.sh</code> file with following content:
    </p>
    <pre><code>
#!/bin/bash
export GPU_FORCE_64BIT_PTR=0
export GPU_MAX_HEAP_SIZE=100
export GPU_USE_SYNC_OBJECTS=1
export GPU_MAX_ALLOC_PERCENT=100
export GPU_SINGLE_ALLOC_PERCENT=100
<kbd>&lt;path to miner&gt;</kbd>/ethminer -F http://sg.clo.epool.network:8888/<kbd>&lt;wallet&gt;</kbd>/<kbd>&lt;worker&gt;</kbd> -G --farm-recheck 200
          </code></pre>
    <p>
      Make it executable: <code>chmod +x &lt;path to .sh file&gt;</code> and run it
    </p>
    <p>
      <code>&lt;wallet&gt;</code> is your CLO wallet address, example:
      <code>0x81029273484ed1167910dd38f7b73000d342f3cf</code>.
      <br>
      <code>&lt;worker&gt;</code> is custom name for worker, example : <code>rig01</code>,
      <code>rig02</code>
    </p>

  </div>

